title: Johnson has 2 TD receptions, leads Colts over Texans 27-20 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,145 Johnson has 2 TD receptions, leads Colts over Texans 27-20 (Yahoo Sports) Andre Johnson proved to his former team that he still has plenty left. Johnson caught two touchdown passes from Matt Hasselbeck, including one for 2 yards in the fourth quarter, to help the Indianapolis Colts beat the Houston Texans 27-20 on Thursday night. Released by Houston in March after 12 seasons with the team, Johnson had six catches for 77 yards.
